name: Iro-Chan
description: IRO-CHAN is a meme coin inspired by Neiro, affectionately nicknamed IRO-CHAN, the sister of the famous Doge Kabosu. Created in memory of Kabosu, who passed away in May 2024, IRO-CHAN aims to honor her legacy by becoming the next big coin on Ethereum. The project focuses on building a strong community and creating a fun, engaging environment for crypto enthusiasts. Embrace the legacy of Doge with IRO-CHAN and join the journey towards becoming a leading meme coin in the crypto space.
